Package io.mpos.transactions

Interface Summary
LocationInformation Collection location information related to the transaction.
ProcessingDetails Identifiers returned by the processor for this transaction.
RefundDetails Refund details of a transaction.
Transaction A transaction contains all information required to make a transaction.
TransactionStatusDetails Object encapsulating details about the current transaction state.
TransactionTemplate A template describing the initial parameters or a transaction.
TransactionTemplateFactory The transaction temnplate factory is used to create a new transaction template that can be used to create a new transaction via the PWCServerSubsystem additions.
 

Enum Summary
Currency The currency used for a transaction.
RefundDetailsProcess Processes required to perform a refund.
RefundDetailsStatus Type of refund allowed for the transaction.
TransactionAction Actions requested during a transaction.
TransactionCardholderVerification The verification used for the transaction.
TransactionState The state of the transaction.
TransactionStatus The final result of the transaction.
TransactionStatusDetailsCodes Enum indicating a more detailed status on the transaction.
TransactionType The type of transaction that will be executed
